oji\" />"},{"pid":"0a33423d3601c761c9c96049557123da610aeb3e","tid":259504,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45005c90d753fddfbed6ed1d2681ea866a26d149","tid":259504,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本好多所謂教師都只係教院畢業，自己對考試都冇咩理解，又點樣教到學生拎高分 ?</blockquote><br />\n跟住個答案教書 <br />\n改卷都有marking scheme 洗鬼用腦"},{"pid":"20c1286d5591322fd2435c6257c20a06f35b2914","tid":259504,"uid":55093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本好多所謂教師都只係教院畢業，自己對考試都冇咩理解，又點樣教到學生拎高分 ?</blockquote><br />\n唔止語文科, 好多理科出身既都只係third hon畢業<br />\nfirst hon果d 9成係大陸仔<br />\n你諗下有冇fresh grad講普通話既會做中學老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家d老師仲要2萬幾3萬起跳<br />\n你話係咪overpaid"},{"pid":"e66bce877d872b85b19c4d7c7fe05310ad3ffa5f","tid":259504,"uid":55093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地個年代唔洗學普通話<br />\n<br />\n唔識有咩咁奇<br />\n<br />\n英文呢D考完就唔記得晒嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n有幾多個真係神人 考完ALCE仲記得內容呀</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知自己up乜尻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n語文科要背內容考試呀?<br />\n你估佢地考緊中史?<br />\n就算係要考背既內容, 你日日都要教書點會唔記得到肥晒佬呀<br />\n仲有你明知要考試都唔識溫下書咪自己抵死囉"},{"pid":"6e1655cf1910c1a7450e1a273c88156cd1b8584b","tid":259504,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前中學個後生英文miss係教院出黎, 仲要教預科<br />\n<br />\n問佢以前會考AL咩成績就死都唔答人<br />\n<br />\n話我依家係老師我一定叻過你地, 你地只要聽我講就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可想而知依家d老師係咩水平</blockquote><br />\n咁佢教得垃唔垃圾？</blockquote><br />\n<b